verbose_text: In addition, the highest concentration of SP (200 mug/mL) showed a cytotoxic effect on HMC-1 cells (about 10% of cells were dead for 12 h), although the amount of IL-8 release in SP (200 mug/mL)-stimulated cells showed a similar level compared with the result of stimulation with 100 mug/mL (data not shown).
